IN RE the PINELANDS COMMISSION'S CONSISTENCY DETERMINATIONS APPROVING TUCKAHOE TURF FARM INC. 'S APPLICATION NO. 1984-0389.009. (Pinelands Preservation Alliance and New Jersey Conservation Foundation - Petitioners) C-413 September Term 2018
081701 Supreme Court of New Jersey. December 17, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-5025-14, A-3417-15 and A-3670-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
